{"abstract":[{"text":"Actor hop은 서로 다른 actor 격리 간 이동 비용입니다. DiContainer는 스냅샷 후 병렬 등록으로 hop을 최소화합니다.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"핵심 아이디어","type":"heading","anchor":"%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC-%EC%95%84%EC%9D%B4%EB%94%94%EC%96%B4"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"스냅샷: 등록할 모듈 배열을 actor 내부에서 복사"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"병렬 처리: TaskGroup으로 비즈니스 로직 등록 실행","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"정리: 완료 후 필요한 만큼만 상태 갱신"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"text":"예시","type":"heading","anchor":"%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let snapshot = modules","await withTaskGroup(of: Void.self) { group in","  for module in snapshot {","    group.addTask { await module.register() }","  }","  await group.waitForAll()","}"]},{"level":2,"text":"베스트 프랙티스","type":"heading","anchor":"%EB%B2%A0%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%ED%94%84%EB%9E%99%ED%8B%B0%EC%8A%A4"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"build() 단계에서만 병렬화"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"등록 시점에는 누적만 하고 즉시 실행하지 않기","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/dicontainer\/actorhopexplanation"]}],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"DiContainer"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"Actor Hop Explanation"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/ActorHopExplanation","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://DiContainer/documentation/DiContainer":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/dicontainer"